					DOTFILES
				My personal configurations
INSTALL
Basically use the makefile.

At the end of installing quicklisp, press ENTER to confirm the installation.

Then, the rest of the files will copy in, and you can exit Emacs once it loads
after downloading everything.

DEPENDENCIES				FOR
	sbcl				SLIME, StumpWM
	clang				company, irony-mode
	cmake				irony-mode
	llvm-libs			irony-mode
	compton				transparency
	firefox				web browser
	GNU emacs			everything
	rxvt-unicode			terminal
	dmenu				application launching
	xfce4-panel			status bar
	devmon				auto mounting devices
	dunst				desktop notification daemon
	NetworkManager and nm-applet	network control
	blueman and blueman-applet	bluetooth
	scrot	    			screenshots
	feh				setting background
	amixer				setting volume
	pulseaudio			volume applet
	xbacklight			setting brightness
	Numix				gtk theme
	DejaVu fonts			system wide font
